Company Overview of Kalmar Pooled Investment Trust - Kalmar "Growth-with-Value" Small Cap Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of June 23, 2017, Kalmar Pooled Investment Trust - Kalmar "Growth-with-Value" Small Cap Fund has gone out of business. Kalmar Pooled Investment Trust - Kalmar "Growth-with-Value" Small Cap Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Kalmar Investments Inc. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the growth and value stocks of small-cap companies, with market capitalization within the range of either the Russell 2000 Growth or the Russell 2000 Index and with a maximum market capitalization of US $3.5 billion. It employs fundamental analysi...
As of June 23, 2017, Kalmar Pooled Investment Trust - Kalmar "Growth-with-Value" Small Cap Fund has gone out of business. Kalmar Pooled Investment Trust - Kalmar "Growth-with-Value" Small Cap Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Kalmar Investments Inc. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the growth and value stocks of small-cap companies, with market capitalization within the range of either the Russell 2000 Growth or the Russell 2000 Index and with a maximum market capitalization of US $3.5 billion. It employs fundamental analysis with a focus on factors like significant future business growth, capital appreciation, dynamic, forward-looking companies, strong present and future growth by offering solutions to real problems or innovative products and services, company’s management and controls, profit model, technology, research and development pipeline, competitive positioning, and growth strategy and dynamics to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 2000 Growth Index and the Russell 2000 Index. It employs in house and proprietary research to create its portfolio. Kalmar Pooled Investment Trust - Kalmar "Growth-with-Value" Small Cap Fund was formed on April 11, 1997 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


