 Retirement Plans. Shares of the Fund are available for use in all types of tax-deferred retirement plans such as IRAs, employer-sponsored
defined contribution plans (including 401(k) plans) and tax-sheltered custodial accounts described in Section 403(b)(7) of the Code. Qualified investors benefit from the tax-free compounding of income dividends and capital gains distributions.
